headline: 3 Supercharged Growth Stocks That Billionaires Are Buying
summary: Investors don't have to make guesses about where to put their money in the stock market.  Billionaire investors conduct careful research into every stock they buy, which is why it's worth checking out what they are buying (or selling).  Fortunately, investment firms that manage more than $100 million are required to disclose their holdings with the Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC).
